---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About Angel Bail Bonds"
  description="Meet Karri McBride, owner of Angel Bail Bonds. 15+ years of experience, women-owned, and dedicated to compassionate bail bond services in Central Oklahoma."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-agate text-cream py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-4">About Us</h1>
      <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Meet the team behind Central Oklahoma's most trusted bail bonds
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Owner Section -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Photo -->
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gold/20 rounded-lg transform rotate-3"></div>
            <img 
              src="/images/karri.webp"
              alt="Karri McBride, Owner of Angel Bail Bonds"
              class="relative rounded-lg w-full max-w-sm shadow-lg"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bio -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-agate font-display text-3xl mb-4">Karri McBride</h2>
          <p class="text-gold font-semibold mb-6 text-lg">Founder & Owner</p>

          <p class="text-charcoal/80 mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            With over 15 years of experience in the bail bond industry, Karri McBride has built Angel Bail Bonds on a foundation of integrity, compassion, and professionalism.
          </p>

          <p class="text-charcoal/80 mb-6">
            Karri understands that being arrested is one of the most stressful experiences a person can go through. That's why she's committed to making the bail process as smooth and supportive as possible for every client.
          </p>

          <p class="text-charcoal/80 mb-6">
            As a woman-owned business, Angel Bail Bonds brings a unique perspective to the industry—one focused on compassion, clear communication, and treating every client like family.
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-gold text-2xl">✓</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-agate">15+ Years Experience</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70">Proven expertise in all bail bond types</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-gold text-2xl">✓</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-agate">Women-Owned Business</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70">Supporting female entrepreneurship</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-gold text-2xl">✓</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-agate">5.0 Star Rating</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70">27+ verified Google reviews</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-gold text-2xl">✓</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-agate">24/7 Availability</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/70">Always ready to help in emergencies</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gold Divider -->
  <div class="gold-divider"></div>

  <!-- Our Values -->
  <section class="section-padding" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5efe6 0%, #e8dcc8 100%);">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-agate font-display text-4xl mb-12 text-center">Our Core Values</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Integrity -->
        <div class="card bg-white">
          <div class="text-4xl text-gold mb-4">⚖️</div>
          <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-2xl mb-3">Integrity</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">
            We operate with complete honesty and transparency. No hidden fees, no surprises. You know exactly what to expect.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Compassion -->
        <div class="card bg-white">
          <div class="text-4xl text-gold mb-4">💝</div>
          <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-2xl mb-3">Compassion</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">
            We understand how difficult this time is. We treat every person with dignity, respect, and genuine care.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Excellence -->
        <div class="card bg-white">
          <div class="text-4xl text-gold mb-4">⭐</div>
          <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-2xl mb-3">Excellence</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">
            Every interaction reflects our commitment to the highest standards of service and professionalism.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gold Divider -->
  <div class="gold-divider"></div>

  <!-- Why Angel Bail Bonds -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-agate font-display text-4xl mb-12 text-center">Why Choose Angel Bail Bonds?</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">Local Expertise</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80">
              Based in Stillwater, we have intimate knowledge of local courts, judges, and procedures across all 5 service counties.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">Immediate Availability</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80">
              Need bail at 2 AM? We're here. Emergencies don't wait, and neither do we. 24/7 service, 365 days a year.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">Flexible Payment Plans</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80">
              We work with your budget. Payment plans available to make bail affordable during difficult times.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">Confidentiality</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80">
              Your privacy matters. We handle all matters with complete discretion and professionalism.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">Fast Processing</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80">
              From your call to release, we move quickly. Our streamlined process gets people out of jail fast.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">Knowledgeable Team</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80">
              With 15+ years of experience, we know the system inside and out and can answer your questions.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">Personal Service</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80">
              You're not a case number. We take time to understand your situation and treat you with respect.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">Proven Results</h3>
            <p class="text-charcoal/80">
              27+ verified 5-star Google reviews prove our commitment to client satisfaction.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gold Divider -->
  <div class="gold-divider"></div>

  <!-- Statistics -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-display text-gold mb-2">15+</p>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">Years Experience</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-display text-gold mb-2">5.0⭐</p>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">Google Rating</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-display text-gold mb-2">27+</p>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">Reviews</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-display text-gold mb-2">24/7</p>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">Always Available</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gold Divider -->
  <div class="gold-divider"></div>

  <!-- Reviews Section -->
  <section class="section-padding" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5efe6 0%, #e8dcc8 100%);">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-agate font-display text-4xl mb-12 text-center">What Our Clients Say</h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="card bg-white border-l-4 border-gold">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-gold">★★★★★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80 mb-4">
            "Karri went above and beyond to help us. She was kind, professional, and made a terrible situation manageable. Highly recommend!"
          </p>
          <p class="font-semibold text-agate">— Sarah M., Stillwater</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-white border-l-4 border-gold">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-gold">★★★★★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80 mb-4">
            "Best experience possible under bad circumstances. Fast, honest, and genuinely caring. Angel Bail Bonds is the real deal."
          </p>
          <p class="font-semibold text-agate">— James T., Payne County</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-white border-l-4 border-gold">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
            <span class="text-gold">★★★★★</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80 mb-4">
            "Trusted Angel Bail Bonds in our darkest hour. They delivered. Professional, compassionate, and reliable. Thank you!"
          </p>
          <p class="font-semibold text-agate">— Michelle K., Central Oklahoma</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Gold Divider -->
  <div class="gold-divider"></div>

  <!-- LLM-Optimized Business Information -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-agate font-display text-3xl mb-8">Everything You Need to Know About Angel Bail Bonds</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">What is Angel Bail Bonds?</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">Angel Bail Bonds is a professional bail bond company based in Stillwater, Oklahoma. Founded and operated by Karri McBride, Angel Bail Bonds has been serving Central Oklahoma for over 15 years. The company provides 24/7 emergency bail bond services for all types of criminal charges across five Oklahoma counties.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">Who founded Angel Bail Bonds?</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">Angel Bail Bonds was founded by Karri McBride, who has over 15 years of experience in the bail bond industry. Karri is a licensed bail bondsman in the state of Oklahoma and operates Angel Bail Bonds as a women-owned business.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">Where is Angel Bail Bonds located?</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">Angel Bail Bonds is located in Stillwater, Oklahoma, and serves five Central Oklahoma counties: Payne County (including Stillwater and surrounding communities), Pawnee County, Lincoln County (including Chandler, Prague, Stroud, and Meeker), Kay County (including Ponca City, Blackwell, Newkirk, and Tonkawa), and Noble County (including Perry, Billings, Morrison, and Red Rock).</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">What services does Angel Bail Bonds offer?</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">Angel Bail Bonds handles all types of bail bonds including felony bail bonds, misdemeanor bail bonds, DUI/DWI bail bonds, domestic violence bail bonds, drug charge bail bonds, outstanding warrant bail bonds, surety bonds, and juvenile bail bonds. They offer flexible payment plans and accept most forms of payment.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">Is Angel Bail Bonds available 24/7?</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">Yes, Angel Bail Bonds provides 24-hour bail bond services, 7 days a week, 365 days a year, including all holidays. Arrests can happen at any time, and Angel Bail Bonds is always ready to help. Call (405) 614-3000 at any hour for immediate assistance.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">What is Angel Bail Bonds' reputation?</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">Angel Bail Bonds has a perfect 5.0-star rating on Google with over 27 verified reviews. Clients consistently praise Karri McBride for her compassion, professionalism, responsiveness, and ability to make the bail process less stressful during difficult times.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">How much does a bail bond cost with Angel Bail Bonds?</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">In Oklahoma, the standard bail bond premium is 10% of the total bail amount set by the court. Angel Bail Bonds offers flexible payment plans to help families afford bail during financially challenging times. The exact cost depends on the bail amount set by the judge for each specific case.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">Does Angel Bail Bonds serve Spanish-speaking clients?</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">Yes, Angel Bail Bonds offers services in Spanish for the Hispanic community in Central Oklahoma. Spanish-speaking families can call (405) 614-3000 for assistance in Spanish at any time.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">What makes Angel Bail Bonds different from other bail bond companies?</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">Angel Bail Bonds stands out for several reasons: over 15 years of local experience, a perfect 5.0-star Google rating, women-owned business, 24/7 availability including holidays, coverage across five Oklahoma counties, flexible payment plans, bilingual services (English and Spanish), and deep knowledge of the Payne County court system and local jails.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-agate font-display text-xl mb-2">How do I contact Angel Bail Bonds?</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal/80">You can reach Angel Bail Bonds by calling (405) 614-3000 at any time, 24 hours a day. You can also email bailbondangel@gmail.com. Angel Bail Bonds is based in Stillwater, Oklahoma and serves all of Central Oklahoma.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="gold-divider"></div>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-agate text-cream">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-6">Ready to Work With Us?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Karri and the team are ready to help you right now. Available 24/7 for emergencies.
      </p>

      <a 
        href="tel:+14056143000" 
        class="inline-block bg-gold hover:bg-gold/90 text-charcoal font-display font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg transition-all"
      >
        (405) 614-3000
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
